NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
P.D., Defendant-Petitioner,
and
A.W., Defendant. In the Matter of the Guardianship of S.D., Minor-Respondent. C-1038 September Term 2017
080335 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 20, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005437-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
